I made a chimera's mouth out of sand. xD

I am at day camp all summer as a counselor in training, so I haven’t been home to really… well, draw. However, I do some things in Arts and Crafts, and today we did balloon-people. I however, took a different take. Made with: a red balloon, red, yellow and purple construction paper, and puffballs/feathers for the birdy. :3

Phew, well this took a bit. Here's my entry, a split picture with Fourside on one side, and Moonside on the other. Ness is split in half on both sides. :) I wanted to do something different and use watercolors and markers combined for this one, I hope it turned out alright! The Paper size is 10x11, roughly the same size as 'Onett Rebellion'. I tried to include various enemies in scenes within this GPP.
